you can do for me.

381
00:29:50,221 --> 00:29:53,247
- What?
- You can take this family off my hands.

382
00:29:53,324 --> 00:29:55,588
I ought to be on a boat right now,
bound for Venice.

383
00:29:55,660 --> 00:29:57,594
What's Venice got to do with it?

384
00:29:57,662 --> 00:30:01,291
Plenty. I've got an idea they understand
a guy with a lute over there.

385
00:30:01,366 --> 00:30:04,699
It's too bad that nobody understands you
over here.

386
00:30:04,769 --> 00:30:08,034
Do you know what will happen if this
family is left to their own devices?

387
00:30:08,106 --> 00:30:10,165
Oh, I imagine they'll
struggle along all right.

388
00:30:10,241 --> 00:30:13,369
Of course if you could convince me
that you can support them properly.

389
00:30:13,444 --> 00:30:16,538
- Support them?
- Mm-hmm. Are you married?

390
00:30:16,614 --> 00:30:18,047
No, I'm sane.

391
00:30:19,317 --> 00:30:21,512
Well, have you anybody at all
that you have to take care of?

392
00:30:21,586 --> 00:30:23,281
Yeah... me...

393
00:30:23,354 --> 00:30:25,686
and I'm not picking up anybody else.

394
00:30:25,757 --> 00:30:28,225
You're not gonna stick me
with a kid and an old man.

395
00:30:29,727 --> 00:30:32,321
The first time I met you, I said
some things that I shouldn't have...

396
00:30:32,397 --> 00:30:34,388
so I came here to apologize.

397
00:30:34,465 --> 00:30:37,127
But I see now I was right
the first time.

398
00:30:37,202 --> 00:30:38,897
Hey, my lute!

399
00:31:08,766 --> 00:31:10,825
What's the trouble?

400
00:31:10,902 --> 00:31:13,735
I thought you were
my most intimate friend.

401
00:31:13,805 --> 00:31:16,205
Well, who said I wasn't?

402
00:31:16,274 --> 00:31:18,572
I heard you tell her
that you don't want me.

403
00:31:18,643 --> 00:31:22,909
Well, I had to tell her something
to get rid of her, didn't I?

404
00:31:22,981 --> 00:31:25,245
And I heard you tell her
you were gonna leave us.

405
00:31:28,219 --> 00:31:30,084
Why don't you be reasonable?
Look.

406
00:31:30,154 --> 00:31:33,612
How long do you want me to hang around,
and why do you want me to?

407
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:37,751
I've fallen in love with you.

408
00:31:41,199 --> 00:31:43,133
When did this happen?

409
00:31:46,104 --> 00:31:50,700
When you got me these. And I'll give
them to you if you'll only stay.

410
00:31:52,477 --> 00:31:55,344
You're the worst pest
I ever ran into.

411
00:31:55,413 --> 00:31:57,347
Come on. Get outta there.

412
00:32:02,987 --> 00:32:04,420
Alley-oop.

413
