Now listen.

861
01:06:02,858 --> 01:06:05,622
I know you got other things
to think about...

862
01:06:05,695 --> 01:06:09,722
but can't you find some way
to get me out of here?

863
01:06:09,799 --> 01:06:11,061
Can't you think of something?

864
01:06:11,133 --> 01:06:16,332
- <i>Be sure that your umbrella</i>
- Can't you...

865
